{"tid":1715142,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"【緊急】三罷做漏咗一樣野","createTime":"2019-11-13T04:27:36.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-13T10:40:52.000Z","uid":47639,"like":29,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"b5d04268fc44586fe646b8c498c7193f87cbfb2d","tid":1715142,"uid":47639,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T04:27:36.000Z","msg":"就係<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">文宣</span></span><br />\n<br />\n現時極度欠缺適合<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">極淺黃/和理非</span></span>睇既文宣/行動 綜合解釋返<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">三罷既合理性</span></span> 並向受影響人士<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">致歉</span></span><br />\n<br />\n我明白有人會認為 要變黃一早變左黃 但無可否認 香港依然有大量中間派 而呢堆人既特點係認為遊行示威表達訴求ok 但始終都不應破壞 <br />\n<br />\n而近日示威者係電視/各大新聞都充斥暴力畫面(e.g. 火魔法, 破壞商場店舖) 而家三罷塞鐵睇到大家對受影響市民既態度係冇85咁有禮貌 對於呢班人黎講係會反感(利申 本人絕對不割 支持前線手足一切行動) <br />\n<br />\n呢班人如果睇得多紅媒就會慢慢變藍 我地唔可以只係圍爐整適合自己友睇既野 更加要吸納中間派 得到佢地既支持<br />\n<br />\n請唔好忽視民意戰 三罷要打得靚 民意戰都唔可以輸 對家已經出手<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/haD74QJ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FhaD74QJ.jpg&h=b7075d5e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n文宣建議方式:<br />\n<br />\n1. 以文章/懶人包取代圖片<br />\n<br />\n呢班中立派多數都認為自己係理性分析每一件事 圖片難以提供足夠資訊說服佢地 要以懶人包/文章詳細論述三罷合理性)<br />\n<br />\n2. 大量例證<br />\n<br />\n文宣應加以證據確鑿既事實做例證 (e.g.輪姦案 我信好大可能係事實 但不能作為有效例證 因為未有確實證據)<br />\n<br />\n係時候反擊 做大量呢類型既<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">三罷文宣</span></span> <span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">瘋傳</span></span>比身邊既<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">中立派</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">光復香港 時代革命</span></strong></span>"},{"pid":"6fd646dc63c9deb23f3c3727108fb906442e2cdd","tid":1715142,"uid":47639,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T04:28:53.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"7f4d3e41e099dd90d551c763778e10cc16055efd","tid":1715142,"uid":47639,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T04:29:26.000Z","msg":"有錯請指教<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5b07775c9b00382e9d97fa69fd1ebff09d1e2e53","tid":1715142,"uid":47639,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T04:29:36.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"5c7593e29e5c832c07202bb690b079c661b85524","tid":1715142,"uid":331879,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T04:30:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0f937071da6286919e82fd6f6cfd794d3b2b6de2","tid":1715142,"uid":47639,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T04:30:36.000Z","msg":"跪求文宣組發功<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6c0ae6a3d4f340dc0bee212b31596339ea857448","tid":1715142,"uid":47639,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T04:31:16.000Z","msg":"覺得啱既請正皮幫推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8f2926